I only have podman configured on user level, so `/etc/containers/containers.conf` does not exist for me.
My `~/.config/containers/containers.conf`only contains a setting for the `dns_bind_port`:
```
[network]
dns_bind_port = 1153
```

> What is the output of podman unshare --rootless-netns nft list ruleset when you have both containers running?

Complains about `nft` not being available in PATH. I guess because i am not using nftables on my host system. Running the command in a nix shell, i get this:

